acceptance_criteria: pm brief prompt exists; output is deterministic and token-aware; tests cover prompt rendering and command registration; README documents usage; release check passes.
resolution: Agent handoff prompt command and renderer added.
expected_result: Agents can generate a compact copy-pasteable handoff prompt from pm state.
actual_result: "Command registered, prompt renderer tested, README documented, and npm run release:check passed."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-12T13:56:07.127Z",unknown,"Implemented pm brief prompt with deterministic copy-pasteable agent handoff output. Updated tests to cover command registration and prompt rendering, updated README usage, and ran npm run release:check successfully: 11 node:test tests passed, npm audit --omit=dev found 0 vulnerabilities, npm pack --dry-run succeeded, changelog check passed."
